channel.title: The DAISy Lab @ NC State
channel.description: Recent content on The DAISy Lab @ NC State

item.description: Nicole is a 4th year undergraduate student at NC State, working towards a B.S. in Computer Engineering and minoring in Art and Design. She is currently conducting signal processing and computer vision research, working on fisheye and stereo image processing. She focuses her studies on the intersection of art and science, more specifically, exploring the impact of perspective and our assumptions in the sciences.
